07:24.835 --> 07:26.315
"Once upon a time,

07:26.358 --> 07:28.535
there was a unicorn
named Eleanor.

07:28.578 --> 07:30.275
She wasn't like
the other unicorns

07:30.319 --> 07:33.278
because she had two horns.

07:35.063 --> 07:36.151
There's the wizard,

07:36.194 --> 07:37.500
he says he can help her,

07:37.544 --> 07:39.197
but only if she finds

07:39.241 --> 07:40.416
someone else like her.

07:40.460 --> 07:41.809
So she wanders around

07:41.852 --> 07:43.027
until she finds a knight

07:43.071 --> 07:44.507
who's stuck in a tree.

07:44.551 --> 07:45.769
He's lonely, too,

07:45.813 --> 07:48.337
and his name is Francis.

07:51.340 --> 07:52.559
And they go back to the wizard

07:52.602 --> 07:54.778
so he can make her normal.

07:56.084 --> 07:57.215
But then the wizard says

07:57.259 --> 07:58.782
that she's better than normal,

07:58.826 --> 08:00.741
she's special.

08:00.784 --> 08:02.307
And now that
she has another friend,

08:02.351 --> 08:03.961
she's not lonely."

08:04.005 --> 08:05.528
And that's it. The end.

08:06.747 --> 08:08.792
