09:17.382 --> 09:19.341
eighteen alligator,

09:19.384 --> 09:20.951
nineteen alligator...

09:24.302 --> 09:25.869
twenty alligator...

09:29.960 --> 09:31.527
twenty-one alligator,

09:32.441 --> 09:34.922
twenty-two alligator.

