16:15.017 --> 16:16.323
they get rotten so fast

16:16.366 --> 16:18.281
and you never got to finish it.

16:18.325 --> 16:22.155
So, don't be mad.

16:22.198 --> 16:23.373
Okay?

16:24.635 --> 16:25.854
Paul?

16:36.908 --> 16:39.128
